                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Ofanius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Col</abbr><ex>lina</ex></expan> Valens <lb n="3"/>Cyrr<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>le</abbr><ex>gionis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>XV <expan><abbr>Apoll</abbr><ex>inaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> VIII <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> XXX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <lb n="7"/>Capretanus <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> eius<lb break="no" n="9"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Giebel mit Akanthus und Rosetten. Z. 10 befindet sich unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes. Z. 2 (Ende): Buchstabe S oberhalb der Zeile eingefügt. Z. 4, 7 u. 8 (Ende): Die letzten Buchstaben befinden sich teilweise oder ganz auf dem Rahmen. (B): HIld; Vorbeck; Krüger: Z. 3: le[g(ionis)]; Vorbeck: Z. 5: ann(orum).</p>
            </div>
